  "texts": [
    "Even if those were fixed, the PyChrono script would produce nonphysical motion.",
    "Some of the issues noted are as follows:1.",
    "API family mixing and hallucinations.",
    "The code blends legacy and modern Chrono APIs (e.g., ChVectorD vs. ChVector3d) and calls nonexistent methods such as system.GetGround() and SetWvel par(). 2.",
